title: i need help with multiline CHIQUI
author: fulldesign

comments.content: Very nice find, Ryuk. This one was driving me crazy.
Thanks Mike :) Was lucky for this one because it is actually the only '5 lines' font I know.

Good find, Ryuk. I went up to the root and found [http://mksd.jp/designfont.html](http://web.archive.org/web/20150317051744/http:/mksd.jp/designfont.html "http://mksd.jp/designfont.html") which has some unique offerings in addition to Millenium 5 Lines. Worth the time to browse them. For example Cloooud [http://mksd.jp/cloooud.html](http://web.archive.org/web/20150317051744/http:/mksd.jp/cloooud.html "http://mksd.jp/cloooud.html") is real kawaii.  
Don
